{"tid":407344,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[桌球球例計分疑問區]","createTime":"2017-09-20T11:05:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T11:23:06.000Z","uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b2379bf557cebf22ef6a4ef2671c72330e49bc32","tid":407344,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"我想問<br />\n 1.如果A打色波，打唔入，但入左白波，咁B加幾多分？<br />\n<br />\n2.如果A打色波入左，但入埋白波，咁A加幾多，B又加幾多？"},{"pid":"105f95c5ff521314c8a26dede7462517fdb3d87f","tid":407344,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:07:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問<br />\n 1.如果A打色波，打唔入，但入左白波，咁B加幾多分？<br />\n<br />\n2.如果A打色波入左，但入埋白波，咁A加幾多，B又加幾多？</blockquote><br />\n1. B +4<br />\n2. A +0<br />\n    B +4"},{"pid":"1aa9a5fa110092e75431b0c239ee4cadca86c2eb","tid":407344,"uid":40010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:10:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我想問<br />\n 1.如果A打色波，打唔入，但入左白波，咁B加幾多分？<br />\n<br />\n2.如果A打色波入左，但入埋白波，咁A加幾多，B又加幾多？</blockquote><br />\n1. B +4<br />\n2. A +0<br />\n    B +4</blockquote><br />\n如果個色波係黑柴，係咪+8?"},{"pid":"773786eb85286fac01d0fc614a15982e01dc54df","tid":407344,"uid":23640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:12:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我想問<br />\n 1.如果A打色波，打唔入，但入左白波，咁B加幾多分？<br />\n<br />\n2.如果A打色波入左，但入埋白波，咁A加幾多，B又加幾多？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nFoul最低消費係4度，foul藍波或以上就睇隻顏色波幾多分（e.g. 黑波就7度）<br />\n<br />\n當上面兩個case顏色波係藍波，B都係加5度"},{"pid":"a7c8e8b6e96e2f6e6df3613cfdc3b30d05720598","tid":407344,"uid":6329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:12:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我想問<br />\n 1.如果A打色波，打唔入，但入左白波，咁B加幾多分？<br />\n<br />\n2.如果A打色波入左，但入埋白波，咁A加幾多，B又加幾多？</blockquote><br />\n1. B +4<br />\n2. A +0<br />\n    B +4</blockquote><br />\n如果個色波係黑柴，係咪+8?</blockquote><br />\n黑波7度，所以+7"},{"pid":"6772da63a4f6cc5b3da5d9af907e7e7decb2f162","tid":407344,"uid":10608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:23:06.000Z","msg":"跟顏色罰<br />\n<br />\n至少罰4度"}]}